    Call LOADPIVZON(PITPJT,PWKNBZON,PWKTABZON,PWKTABABR,PWKZON,PWKFRM,PWKWRK) From CONNECTFCT
    Call WRPIVOT_HEAD(PITPJT,PWKNBZON,PWKTABZON,PWKTABABR,PWKZON,PWKWRK,PWKHEATYP,PWKHEADMES,WPREPJT,OPTPJT) From CONNECTFCT
